subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Murray, a 21-year-old from Scotland who is seeded sixth, upended Juan Martín del Potro, a 19-year-old challenger from Argentina, 7-6 (2), 7-6 (1), 4-6, 7-5.
